# Pin a specific upstream commit of github.com/C2SP/wycheproof so the
# runner is reproducible. Bump this SHA when relevant new vectors are
# published upstream and re-run the suite.
#
# How to bump :
#   1. cd tests/wycheproof
#   2. git ls-remote https://github.com/C2SP/wycheproof.git HEAD
#   3. Copy the SHA from the first column into VECTORS_SHA (no newline)
#   4. ./fetch_vectors.sh   # downloads the new tree
#   5. ./run_wycheproof.py  # confirm no regression
#   6. git commit -s -m "tests(wycheproof): bump VECTORS_SHA to <short>"
#
